import React from 'react'
import { Container, Nav, Navbar, NavDropdown } from 'react-bootstrap'

const ChooseCharts = ({ title }) => {
  const [activeChart, setActiveChart] = useState('BarChart')

  const renderActiveChart = () => {
    switch (activeChart) {
      case 'BarChart':
        return <BarChart />
      case 'LineChart':
        return <LineChart />
      case 'PieChart':
        return <PieChart />
      default:
        return null
    }
  }
  return (
    <Navbar expand="lg" className={'custom-navbar'}>
      <Container fluid>
        <Navbar.Brand href="#home">{title}</Navbar.Brand>
        <Navbar.Toggle aria-controls="navbar-dark-example" />
        <Navbar.Collapse id="navbar-dark-example">
          <Nav className="ms-auto">
            <NavDropdown id="nav-dropdown-dark-example" title="Choose a Chart">
              <NavDropdown.Item eventKey="BarChart">Bar Chart</NavDropdown.Item>
              <NavDropdown.Item eventKey="LineChart">
                Line Chart
              </NavDropdown.Item>
              <NavDropdown.Item eventKey="PieChart">Pie Chart</NavDropdown.Item>
            </NavDropdown>
          </Nav>
        </Navbar.Collapse>
      </Container>
    </Navbar>
  )
}

export default ChooseCharts
